This documentation details the Customer.io Cohort Sync integration, which allows businesses to export Amplitude cohorts to Customer.io for targeted messaging campaigns, including setup steps in both platforms, sync process, and considerations such as paid plan requirements and the need for users to exist in Customer.io before syncing.

